0.7.1 (August 4, 2011)
======================

+ #2: Now pkgtools supports extras. (See :attr:`pkgtools.pkg.Dist.requires`.)

0.7 (July 24, 2011)
===================

+ Started writing tests (lettuce).
+ Added new attribute :attr:`location` to :class:`pkgtools.pkg.Dist`.
+ Added a new method :meth:`~pkgtools.pkg.Installed.installed_files` to :class:`pkgtools.pkg.Installed`.

0.6.2 (July 8, 2011)
====================

+ Added special attributes ``_name`` and ``_version`` to :class:`pkgtools.pkg.Dist`.

0.6 (May 26, 2011)
==================

+ Added :func:`pkgtools.pkg.get_metadata`.

0.5
===

+ Added :class:`pkgtools.pkg.WorkingSet`.

0.4
===

+ Added :class:`pkgtools.pkg.EggDir`.

0.3
===

+ Added :class:`pkgtools.pkg.PyPIJson`.

0.1
===

+ First release.